## About Me

I build AI systems that go beyond demos — production-aware pipelines with deliberate engineering trade-offs.

My focus is on **LLM systems**, **multimodal AI**, and **efficient inference** — understanding not just how to make models work, but how to make them work *at scale*. I care about the gap between a notebook prototype and something you can actually ship.

```python
bhavisha = {
    "currently_building": ["LLM pipelines", "multimodal RAG", "agentic systems"],
