## Featured Projects

| Project | What it does | Stack |
|:---|:---|:---|
| [**SDLC_Exploration**](https://github.com/Bhavi15/SDLC_Exploration) | VS Code extension: design files → production code, user stories, BRDs, Playwright tests via Copilot | TypeScript · VS Code LM API |
| [**Multimodal-RAG**](https://github.com/Bhavi15/Multimodal-RAG) | RAG pipeline over medical PDFs — extracts & captions both text and images; single-LLM + multi-agent | Python · LangGraph · FAISS · GROQ |
| [**Deliberative-RAG**](https://github.com/Bhavi15/Deliberative_RAG) | Conflict-aware deep research agent that reasons about contradictions standard RAG ignores | Python · LangChain |
| [**Fine-Tuned-Transformer**](https://github.com/Bhavi15/Fine-Tuned-Transformer-Model) | DistilBERT SFT on 50K IMDB reviews — 92.63% accuracy at 40% of standard BERT inference cost | PyTorch · HuggingFace · W&B |

